        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down.</hi> | Beckenham | <hi rend="print">Kent. S.E.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Nov. 6<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am much obliged to you for your kindness in sending me the interesting fact communicated in your letter.<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>I have not heard of any such case in the human family, but have long suspected that many grey coloured animals have thus originated.</p>
<p>With my best thanks, pray believe me | Dear Sir, yours faithfully | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
